description: On the October 2nd edition of the Cigar Authority, the guys will start up telling you about the SWAG Cigar by Oliveros. You will learn about some history that happened on the date October 2nd. We also welcome in 2 special guests, Jim Falzone and Slater Martin. Now, The Cigar Authority!
